('Cooper Firearms of Montana', 'Model 21', 'Various', 'Rifle', 'Bolt-Action', 4, 1992, false, 'United States', 'Custom bolt-action varmint rifle built on the Kimber-derived Cooper action. Available in a wide range of varmint and small centerfire calibers with premium walnut stocks and hand-lapped barrels.', 1895, 96.0, 42.0, false, false, ARRAY['Model 21 Varmint', 'Model 21 Phoenix', 'Model 21 Western Classic'], 'Active', 'Cooper Model 21', ARRAY['.17 Rem', '.222 Rem', '.223 Rem', '.22 Hornet'], ARRAY['model 21', 'cooper 21'], 'Modern', 'Single-Action', ARRAY['hunting', 'competition'], NULL, 'United States', false, NULL),

